"Apple's system translation sheet stays reachable on artwork captions and comments, gated to skip empty / emoji-only text." = "在作品簡介與留言中保留 Apple 系統翻譯面板入口，並跳過空文本與纯表情。";
"Keep the translatable-text gate in regression coverage so we never surface a no-op Translate button." = "在回歸覆盖中保留可翻譯文本的門控，避免出現無意義的翻譯按钮。";
"CaptionTranslationAvailability accepts Pixiv caption shapes and rejects emoji-only blurbs." = "CaptionTranslationAvailability 接受 Pixiv 簡介格式並拒绝纯表情短文本。";
"Following-artist emphasis" = "已追蹤畫师强調";
"Cards from artists the user follows pick up an accent border and a Following badge in mixed feeds, and the toggle round-trips through UserDefaults." = "已追蹤畫师的作品在混合 feed 中呈現强調色邊框與「已追蹤」徽標，開關狀態通過 UserDefaults 持久化。";
"Keep emphasizeFollowingArtists in lock-step with its persisted value so a profile sync never loses the visual treatment." = "保持 emphasizeFollowingArtists 與其持久化值同步，避免資料同步導致視覺强調丟失。";
"Transferable drag and drop" = "Transferable 拖放";
"Pixiv-link drops resolve through Transferable on every drop surface, and completed downloads + artwork cards drag out as native file or URL payloads." = "所有放置區均通過 Transferable 解析 Pixiv 連結，已完成的下載與作品卡也能以原生檔案或連結形式拖出。";
"Keep PixivLinkDropPayload and the artwork drag URL covered so a future ProxyRepresentation refactor doesn't silently break Finder drops." = "在覆盖中保留 PixivLinkDropPayload 與作品拖拽 URL，避免未來的 ProxyRepresentation 重構悄然破壞訪達拖放。";
"PixivLinkDropPayload resolves URL and text shapes; download rows and artwork cards expose Transferable drag sources." = "PixivLinkDropPayload 解析 URL 與文本兩种形態，下載行與作品卡均提供 Transferable 拖拽源。";
"Quick Look" = "快速查看";
"Press Space to peek the file with Quick Look, just like Finder." = "按下空格鍵即可像訪達一樣用快速查看預覽檔案。";
"Quick Look preview" = "快速查看預覽";
"Completed downloads expose a Quick Look affordance — Space-bar peek, toolbar button, and context-menu entry — that opens Apple's system preview panel." = "已完成的下載提供快速查看入口——空格鍵預覽、工具欄按钮和右鍵菜單項均會調起 Apple 系統預覽面板。";
"Keep DownloadQueueView's quickLookURL binding and focus-driven Space handler covered so Apple's preview panel never falls back to a third-party fallback." = "持續覆盖 DownloadQueueView 的 quickLookURL 绑定與基於焦點的空格鍵處理，確保 Apple 的預覽面板不會回退到第三方實現。";
"Each completed row resolves a Quick Look URL and surfaces the preview button, context-menu entry, and Space-bar handler." = "每個已完成的下載行都能解析出快速查看 URL，並暴露預覽按钮、右鍵菜單項和空格鍵處理。";
"%@/s" = "%@/秒";
"Total %@" = "合計 %@";
"Live download throughput" = "下載速度實時顯示";
"Active downloads display a sliding-window byte-per-second readout per row and an aggregate rate in the queue subtitle, just like Finder." = "下載中的任务在每一行顯示滑動窗口內的每秒字节数，並在隊列副標題中展示總速率，像訪達一樣。";
"Keep DownloadThroughputSampler wired through ArtworkDownloadStore.download(_:sourceURLs:) and reset on pause / cancel / complete so the speedometer never lies." = "保持 DownloadThroughputSampler 接入 ArtworkDownloadStore.download(_:sourceURLs:)，並在暫停/取消/完成時重置，避免速度指示失真。";
"Throughput sampler records per-page bytes and exposes per-item plus aggregate rates that the queue surfaces." = "速率采樣器按頁記錄字节数，並對外暴露單任务和聚合速率，由下載隊列介面展示。";
"Download finished" = "下載已完成";
"Downloads finished" = "下載已完成";
"%d artworks finished downloading." = "%d 個作品已完成下載。";
"Notify when downloads finish" = "下載完成時傳送通知";
"Posts a Notification Center banner once a download wraps up — coalesced for batches so a 50-image queue still surfaces a single banner." = "下載完成後向通知中心推送一条橫幅，批量下載會合並為單条橫幅，避免 50 张圖的隊列產生 50 条通知。";
"Notification Center declined permission. Re-enable banners for KeiPix in System Settings → Notifications." = "通知中心已拒绝授權。請在「系統設定 → 通知」中為 KeiPix 重新開啟橫幅通知。";
"Notification Center banner on download finish" = "下載完成時的通知中心橫幅";
"DownloadCompletionNotifier coalesces completed-download titles into a single banner per quiescent burst, gated on the user's opt-in toggle and Apple's authorization state." = "DownloadCompletionNotifier 會在静默窗口內合並已完成的下載標題為單条橫幅，受使用者開關與 Apple 授權狀態共同控制。";
"Keep ArtworkDownloadStore.markCompleted wired through DownloadCompletionNotifier so a finished download still hands off to UNUserNotificationCenter." = "保持 ArtworkDownloadStore.markCompleted 經由 DownloadCompletionNotifier 轉交給 UNUserNotificationCenter，以便完成的下載仍會觸發通知。";
"Notifier records every markCompleted call and posts one Notification Center request per debounce window." = "通知器在每次 markCompleted 調用時記錄任务，並在防抖窗口內向通知中心傳送一次請求。";
